ICD-10-CM (CMS-published, public domain)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project bundles the FY2026 ICD-10-CM tabular list under
src/phantom_codes/data/icd10cm/ for use by the hallucination validator,
and the CMS ACCESS Model FHIR ValueSets under
src/phantom_codes/data/access_valuesets/ for cohort scope filtering.
Both are public-domain US government works published by the Centers
for Medicare & Medicaid Services. No attribution is legally required;
provenance is recorded here for transparency.

  ICD-10-CM is published by the National Center for Health Statistics
  and CMS, available at:
  https://www.cms.gov/medicare/coding-billing/icd-10-codes

  CMS ACCESS Model FHIR Implementation Guide v0.9.6:
  https://dsacms.github.io/cmmi-access-model/


